A '''Vjun fox''' was a type of vulpine non-[[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] native to [[Vjun/Legends|Vjun]]. It had brindled red and cream fur and prehensile forepaws. One known fox was [[Miss Vix]], who belonged to [[Whirry Malreaux]].

